# UI Components and Design System

This application uses a custom component library built with Tailwind CSS and DaisyUI.

## Core UI Components

- [src/components/ui/Button.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/Button.tsx) - Button component
- [src/components/ui/Input.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/Input.tsx) - Input field component
- [src/components/ui/Label.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/Label.tsx) - Label component
- [src/components/ui/Alert.tsx](mdc:src/components/ui/Alert.tsx) - Alert/notification component

## Layout Components

- [src/components/layout](mdc:src/components/layout) - Application layout components
- [src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:src/app/layout.tsx) - Root layout component

## Design System

- The application uses Tailwind CSS for styling
- The design system is configured in [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js)
- Global styles are defined in [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css)

